      "rendered": "<p>Accurately measuring the performance of marketing efforts is crucial for nonprofits to evaluate and optimize their strategies to make the most of precious resources. Learning how to create and track Conversions in Google Analytics 4 is a must for today&#8217;s digital marketers.</p>\n",
